<h3>Version 1.0.0</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Initial release</li>
    <li>Support for GitHub, Google, Facebook, Twitter/X OAuth</li>
    <li>Generic OAuth 2.0 provider support</li>
    <li>Secure session management with cookie-based authentication</li>
    <li>CSRF protection via state parameter</li>
    <li>Account linking - users can connect multiple providers</li>
    <li>Admin panel for provider configuration</li>
    <li>Customizable login and profile templates</li>
    <li>Events for integration with other modules</li>
    <li>Developer API for checking authentication status</li>
</ul>
